title: Week 5 Recap 2022
description:
Daniel Dopp, Mike Clay and Liz Loza recap everything you need to know from Week 5 of the NFL season including what players will need to be in your lineup going forward. Plus, audio exclusive reaction to a close SNF game including some poor fantasy performances with Liz Loza and Eric Moody.
